My friendship with @deanastanfield is a beautiful thing and here’s why. I think when you can forge a friendship with somebody despite your many differences - your countless, colossal, seemingly insurmountable differences; when you can form a bond with that person, and regard them as “brother”, through love, and empathy..and understanding; well I think that’s just remarkable. Happy Memorial Day everybody.

(I’m on the left in all these pictures btw)
